OL,3,CJails in England and Wales 98.3% full
OL,4,Cas prison crisis continues
OL,6,FPrisons in England and Wales are 98.3%
OL,7,Ffull, despite the population falling
OL,8,Fslightly since the government accepted
OL,9,Frecommendations of a recent sentencing
OL,10,Freview.
OL,12,FThere are now 1,448 prison places
OL,13,Favailable - up from 961 last month,
OL,14,Fwhen the estate was running at 98.9%
OL,15,Fcapacity.
OL,17,FBut HM Prison and Probation Service
OL,18,Fsays it can't run the estate
OL,19,Fefficiently at over 95% occupancy.
