OL,3,CJails in England and Wales 98.3% full
OL,4,Cas prison crisis continues
OL,6,FThe UK's prisons estate has been under
OL,7,Fso much pressure that thousands of
OL,8,Finmates have been released early to
OL,9,Fprevent the system clogging up, a
OL,10,Fsituation that the justice secretary
OL,11,Fwarned could lead to the "break down
OL,12,Fof law and order".
OL,14,FIf prisons are full, police cells
OL,15,Fwould have to be used to house
OL,16,Foffenders - but when they reach
OL,17,Fcapacity, officers would no longer be
OL,18,Fable to carry out arrests, Shabana
OL,19,FMahmood said last month.
