OL,6,FNew policies include allowing well
OL,7,Fbehaved offenders to serve one third
OL,8,Fof their sentence, rather than half
OL,9,Fand scrapping short sentences of less
OL,10,Fthan 12 months, apart from in
OL,11,Fexceptional circumstances such as
OL,12,Fdomestic abuse cases.
OL,14,FThere have also been calls to improve
OL,15,Frehabilitation inside prisons, given
OL,16,F53% of those released commit crime
OL,17,Fagain within a year, while 80% of
OL,18,Foffenders are reoffenders.
